Metadata: 6th National Aquaculture Extension Conference: Oral and poster presentation abstracts
6th National Aquaculture Extension Conference, Boise, Idaho, June 6-8, 2017

Presentations from the 6th National Aquaculture Extension Conference, 2017. Held approximately every five years since 1992, this unique conference has provided a forum for professional development and growth for all levels of experience and years of service in aquaculture extension education.
